OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine or sunny spells. Light winds
OL,7,Fto start, though becoming breezy
OL,8,Flater, especially near coasts.
OL,9,FTemperatures will become widely very
OL,10,Fwarm, locally hot though peak
OL,11,Ftemperatures expected across the south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry and mostly cloudy night
OL,14,Fwith a few clear spells possible.
OL,15,FBreezy to start but winds falling
OL,16,Flight later. Mild, though warm in
OL,17,Ftowns and cities.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
