OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FDry and bright with a light
OL,6,Fbreeze. Plenty of hazy sunshine and
OL,7,Fsunny spells at times. Another hot
OL,8,Fday, similar to Monday.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,11,Fand sunny to end the week. Light
OL,12,Fwinds, though breezier Friday. Hot
OL,13,Fthroughout as temperatures increase.
